high_descs: Turn around and take one step, then turn to the right and walk to the desk.
Pick up the cell phone that is on the second shelf of the desk.
Turn to the left and take one step, then turn to the right to face the desk.
Turn on the lamp on the second shelf of the desk.
anns.task_desc: Look at the cell phone in the lamp light.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the bed, then turn right and walk over to the wooden desk.
Pick up the phone off of the desk.
Turn left and walk towards the bed, then turn right and walk up to the wooden desk.
Turn on the light of the small lamp that is on the wooden desk.
anns.task_desc: Examine a phone in the light of a small lamp.

high_descs: Move to the desk on your left.
Pick up the phone on the shelf next to the lamp.
Bring the phone to the lamp on shelf.
Turn on the lamp on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Examine a phone by the light of a lamp on a shelf.
